<div class="about-card app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
        
    <hr>
        
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <%=image_tag "profilepic.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-img" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"  
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7 about-p">
        <p>I am a Full-Stack Developer with a passion for collaboration, learning new technologies and using my analytical background to solve problems. Prior to transitioning to development, I spent four and a half years in Financial and Operations Analyst roles. Knowing that it would be applicable to my career, I began taking a Python course in my spare time. The class provided a great introduction to the world of coding and inspired me to pursue software development full time. When I'm not coding, I'm usually exercising, reading or exploring San Diego.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <h3>Development Experience</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li> Notch8 | Jr. Software Developer | 2020 </li>
                  <li> Notch8 | Software Development Intern | 2019 </li>
                </ul>	
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <h3>Prior Experience</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li> Verus Investments | Operations Anlayst | 2017-2019 </li>
                  <li> Verus Investments | Financial Analyst  | 2015-2017 </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <h3>Education</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li> LEARN Academy | Full Stack Web Developer in Training | 2019 </li>
                  <li> Gonzaga University | BBA Finance & Economics | 2014 </li>
                </ul>	
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>  
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>

